
<body>
<div id="wrap">
  <div class="header1">
    <div class="logo">
      <%= link_to(image_tag(''),  home_index_path) %>
    </div>
    <div id="menu">
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to '首页', home_index_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '草莓时光', static_pages_about_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '草莓商城',  store_index_url %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '莓味佳肴',  recipe_blog_index_url %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '特品草莓园',  static_pages_agencygarden_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '草莓故事',  static_pages_story_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '最新资讯',  static_pages_newslist_path %></li>
        <li class="selected"><%= link_to '莓园联盟',  static_pages_alliance_garden_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '联系我们', static_pages_contact_path %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="center_content">
    <div class="left_content">

      <div class="title"><span class="title_icon"><%= image_tag('bullet1.gif') %></span>莓园联盟</div>


      <div class="feat_prod_box">

        <div class="prod_det_box1">
          <div class="box_top1"></div>
          <div class="box_center1">
            <div class="prod_title">莓园联盟</div>
            <p class="details">
            <p>
              <%= image_tag('aboutST.jpg', :alt=>'MUZT团队的草莓时光', :title=>'', :class=>'right', :width => '150') %>
            <p>    MUZT团队正在努力建设中，敬请期待。</p>
            <p>    如果您是草莓粉，同时了解一些正品有机草莓种植园或草莓制品深加工企业信息，非常欢迎您参与贡献，为草莓粉们提供更多草莓园信息。</p>

            <p>如果您是正品有机草莓种植园经营者或草莓制品深加工企业，非常欢迎您提交详细资料，让广大草莓粉能够了解到您。</p>
            <p>请点击“提交草莓园信息”，来提交信息。</p>
            <div><%= button_to '提交草莓园信息', static_pages_input_garden_info_url %></div>

            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="box_bottom1"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>

      <p></p>
      <div>       <!--Start of alliance_garden index list -->
        <table>
          <% @alliance_gardens.each do |alliance_garden| %>
            <tr class="<%= cycle('list_line_odd', 'list_line_even') %>">

              <td class="list_description">
                <dl>
                  <dt><%= alliance_garden.title %></dt>
                  <dd><%= truncate(strip_tags(alliance_garden.content), :length => 200) %></dd>
                </dl>
              </td>

              <td class="list_actions">
                <%= link_to '浏览详情', alliance_garden, :url => {:controller => 'newslists', :action => 'show', :target=>'_blank' } %><br/>

              </td>

            </tr>

          <% end %>
        </table>

        <br/>
        <%= paginate @alliance_gardens, :left => 2, :right => 3 %>
      </div>       <!--End of alliance_garden index list -->

    </div><!--end of left content-->


    </div><!--end of left content-->



    <div class="right_content">

      <%= render 'layouts/right_down_form' %>


    </div><!--end of right content-->


    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div><!--end of center content-->



</div>

</body>